nl.tno.stormcv.fetcher

Interface IFetcher<Output extends CVParticle>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Serializable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    FetchAndOperateFetcher, FileFrameFetcher, ImageFetcher, RefreshingImageFetcher, StreamFrameFetcher

    public interface IFetcher<Output extends CVParticle>
extends Serializable
    Fetcher implementations are executed within CVParticleSpout and are responsible to read data and push it into topologies. Fetcher's produce a CVParticle implementation which has its own CVParticleSerializer implementation as well.
    Author:
    Corne Versloot
